data.description: Motivated Seller!   Highly sought after 1,384 sq. ft. Sandalwood model in Sun City Summerlin Premier 55+ Community!  Immaculate home with hard-to-find ELEVATED and OVER-SIZED lot offering maximum privacy.  Gorgeous mountain views and low maintenance living!  Well-appointed kitchen with solid surface counter tops and easy-care flooring.  Roomy primary suite with walk-in closet and shower.  Separate living and dining rooms, and a large eat-in kitchen nook nestled into a relaxing bay window. Sun City Summerlin Senior community boasts 3 Golf Courses and many amenities including 4 indoor/outdoor pools, gyms, sports courts, social clubs and more.   *New AC*  Cabinet storage on both sides of garage.
